1. *Radite* da biste uspeli. (You work to succeed.)
2. Oni su *radili* tokom cele noći. (They were working throughout the night.)
3. Vi ćete *raditi* u skladu sa planom. (You will work in accordance with the plan.)
4. *Radila* sam sve što sam mogla da bih zaradila za život. (I worked everything I could to make a living.)
5. Oni će *raditi* do kasno u noć. (They will work late into the night.)
6. Budite spremni da *radite* naporno. (Be prepared to work hard.)